# Margin6 core

Read and follow [`AGENTS.md`](../../AGENTS.md). It is the **only** canonical instruction file for product scope, security, calculations, testing, migrations, and documentation hierarchy.

**Product:** Margin6 — independent restaurant groups (~2–10 locations). **Internal-demo ready; trust repair in progress.**

**Workflow:** Count → Approve → Smart Order → PO → Invoice → Receipt → Dashboard/Alerts

**Rules:**
- Inspect before editing; report drift before fixing
- One epic / one branch / one PR
- Do not rebuild `[AUDIT]` items already implemented
- Do not trust archived docs, ZIPs, or AI summaries over code + live Supabase
- No production migrations, deploys, or broad grant revokes without explicit approval

**Status docs:** [`docs/status/current-product-status.md`](../../docs/status/current-product-status.md)
